# PM Brain has no runtime dependencies and reads no env vars out of the box.
#
# This file is a hook for forks that extend the repo with custom scripts or MCP
# tools that need API keys. Copy to `.env` locally (gitignored) and uncomment
# anything you actually need.
#
# Examples (uncomment if a fork uses them):
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
